de]], Netherlands || {{fbw|ENG}} ||align=center| '''1'''\u20130 ||align=center| 3\u20130\n|-\n| 44. ||rowspan=2| 6 August 2017 ||rowspan=2| De Grolsch Veste, Enschede, Netherlands ||rowspan=2| {{fbw|DEN}} ||align=center| '''1'''\u20131 ||align=center rowspan=2| 4\u20132\n|-\n| 45. ||align=center| '''4'''\u20132\n|-\n| 46. || 19 October 2017 || [[NV Arena]], [[Sankt P\u00f6lten]], Austria || {{fbw|AUT}} ||align=center| '''2'''\u20130 ||align=center| 2\u20130 || [[Exhibition game|Friendly]]\n|-\n| 47. || 24 October 2017 || [[Euroborg]], [[Groningen]], Netherlands || {{fbw|NOR}} ||align=center| '''1'''\u20130 ||align=center| 1\u20130 || rowspan=5| [[2019 FIFA Women's World Cup qualification \u2013 UEFA Group 3|2019 FIFA Women's World Cup qualification]]\n|-\n| 48. ||rowspan=2| 24 November 2017 ||rowspan=2| [[NTC Senec]], [[Senec, Slovakia|Senec]], Slovakia ||rowspan=2| {{fbw|SVK}} ||align=center| '''3'''\u20130 ||align=center rowspan=2| 5\u20130\n|-\n| 49. ||align=center| '''4'''\u20130\n|-\n| 50. || 6 April 2018 || [[Philips Stadion]], [[Eindhoven]], Netherlands ||{{Nowrap|{{fbw|NIR}}}} ||align=center| '''3'''\u20130 ||align=center| 7\u20130\n|-\n| 51. || 4 September 2018 || [[Intility Arena]], [[Oslo]], Norway || {{fbw|NOR}} ||align=center| '''1'''\u20132 ||align=center| 1\u20132\n|-\n| 52. || 9 November 2018 || [[Stadion Galgenwaard]], [[Utrecht]], Netherlands || {{fbw|SWI}} || align=center| '''3'''\u20130 ||align=center| 3\u20130 || rowspan=2| [[2019 FIFA Women's World Cup qualification \u2013 UEFA play-offs|2019 FIFA Women's World Cup qualification play-offs]]\n|-\n| 53. || 13 November 2018 || [[LIPO Park Schaffhausen|LIPO Park]], [[Schaffhausen]], Switzerland || {{fbw|SWI}} || align=center| '''1'''\u20130 || align=center| 1\u20131\n|-\n| 54. || 19 January 2019 || [[Green Point Stadium]], [[Cape Town]], South Africa || {{fbw|RSA}} || align=center| '''2'''\u20130 || align=center| 2\u20131 || [[Exhibition game|Friendly]]\n|-\n| 55. || 6 March 2019 || Est\u00e1dio Mu