0 ||align=center rowspan=2| 8\u20130 \n|-\n| 67. ||align=center| '''5'''\u20130\n|-\n| 68. ||rowspan=2| 12 November 2019 || rowspan=2| [[GelreDome]], [[Arnhem]], Netherlands ||rowspan=2 | {{fbw|SLO}} || align=center| '''3'''\u20131 ||align=center rowspan=2| 4\u20131 \n|-\n| 69. ||align=center| '''4'''\u20131\n|-\n|}\n\n==Honours==\n\n===Club===\n'''Bayern Munich'''\n* [[Bundesliga (women)|Bundesliga]]: [[2014\u201315 Bundesliga (women)|2014\u201315]], [[2015\u201316 Bundesliga (women)|2015\u201316]]\n\n'''Arsenal'''\n* [[FA WSL]]: [[2018\u201319 FA WSL|2018\u201319]]\n* [[FA WSL Cup]]: [[2017\u201318 FA WSL Cup|2017\u201318]]\n\n===International===\n* [[UEFA Women's Under-19 Championship]]: [[2014 UEFA Women's Under-19 Championship|2014]]\n* [[UEFA Women's Euro]]: [[UEFA Women's Euro 2017|2017]]\n* [[FIFA Women's World Cup]] runners-up: [[2019 FIFA Women's World Cup|2019]]\n\n===Individual===\n* [[BeNe League]] Top scorer: [[2013\u201314 BeNe League|2013\u201314]]\n* [[UEFA Women's Under-19 Championship]] Top scorer: [[2014 UEFA Women's Under-19 Championship|2014]]\n* [[UEFA Women's Under-19 Championship]] Golden Player: [[2014 UEFA Women's Under-19 Championship|2014]]\n* [[UEFA Women's Champions League]]: Top scorer: [[2016\u201317 UEFA Women's Champions League|2016\u201317]]\n* London Football Awards Women's Player of the Year: 2019<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://londonfootballawards.org/|title=The London Football Awards 2019 \u2013 Celebrating the very best of London Football|website=londonfootballawards.org|access-date=2019-03-01}}</ref>\n* PFA Players' Player of the Year: 2018\u201319<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.thepfa.com/thepfa/pfa-awards|title=The PFA|website=www.thepfa.com|access-date=2019-07-07}}</ref><ref>{{Citation|last=Evening Standard|title=PFA Awards 2019 live stream {{!}} Van Dijk wins POTY|date=2019-04-28|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dB1JYv6IoAc|access-date=2019-07-07}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist|30em}}\n\n==External links==\n{{commons